      fromHandle: "BYTE_RUNNER"
      toName: "All"
      subject: "Estate sale jackpot!"
      body:
        '''
        Just got back from an estate sale and I can barely contain myself.
        An old electronics technician passed away and his family was selling
        everything.

        I got:
        - Apple IIe with DuoDisk drive
        - Tandy 1000 SX
        - Two Commodore VIC-20s (both working!)
        - A box of mixed 5.25" floppies
        - An oscilloscope from 1978

        Total cost: $60. SIXTY DOLLARS. I am vibrating with excitement.
        '''
