  // ─── Bulletins ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

  bulletins: [
    {
      number: 1
      title: "Welcome to The Neon Underground"
      body:
        '''
        |09===============================================
        |11  W E L C O M E   T O
        |13  T H E   N E O N   U N D E R G R O U N D
        |09===============================================

        |07This bulletin board system has been in
        |07continuous operation since |151994|07.

        |07We are a community of |11retro computing
        |11enthusiasts|07, |13programmers|07, and |10digital
        |10archaeologists|07.

        |08Whether you're a seasoned veteran of the
        |08BBS scene or a curious newcomer, you are
        |08welcome here.

        |07Explore the message areas. Play the door
        |07games. Leave a one-liner. Make yourself
        |07at home.

        |09The SysOp is always here.

        |08               — |15AXIOM|08, SysOp
        '''
    }
    {
      number: 2
      title: "System Rules and Guidelines"
      body:
        '''
        |09===============================================
        |11  S Y S T E M   R U L E S
        |09===============================================

        |151.|07 Be respectful to all users.
        |152.|07 No illegal content. Period.
        |153.|07 One account per person.
        |154.|07 Don't share your password.
        |155.|07 Report bugs to the SysOp.
        |156.|07 Do not browse system directories.
        |157.|07 Do not discuss system operations.

        |09-----------------------------------------------

        |10ETIQUETTE:|07

        |08- Keep messages on-topic in each area.
        |08- Use meaningful subject lines.
        |08- Don't post the same thing everywhere.
        |08- Quote only what's relevant in replies.
        |08- Be patient — this isn't Discord.

        |09-----------------------------------------------

        |14All system activity is monitored and logged.
        |14This is for the safety of all users.

        |08Violations will result in immediate and
        |08permanent access revocation.

        |12There are no second chances.
        |12There are no exceptions.
        '''
    }
    {
      number: 3
      title: "About the SysOp"
      body:
        '''
        |09===============================================
        |13  A B O U T   T H E   S Y S O P
        |09===============================================

        |07Handle:    |15AXIOM
        |07Location:  |08Unknown
        |07Online:    |08Always

        |09-----------------------------------------------

        |07The SysOp of The Neon Underground has been
        |07maintaining this board since its inception
        |07in 1994.

        |08Not much is known about AXIOM. They rarely
        |08post outside of system announcements. They
        |08don't engage in casual conversation. They
        |08don't attend meetups or swap meets. They
        |08have never been seen on any other board.

        |07Some say the board |11is|07 the SysOp.
        |08Some say the SysOp |11is|08 the board.

        |14If you need assistance, leave a message in
        |14the SysOp Announcements area. Your message
        |14will be seen.

        |08Everything here is seen.

        |09===============================================
        '''
    }
    {
      number: 4
      title: "Maintenance Schedule"
      body:
        '''
        |09===============================================
        |11  M A I N T E N A N C E
        |09===============================================

        |07The system undergoes scheduled maintenance
        |07every |15Friday|07 from |1500:00|07 to |1503:00|07 local
        |07server time.

        |09-----------------------------------------------

        |08During this window:

        |08- All active sessions will be terminated
        |08- New connections will not be accepted
        |08- The system will not respond to probes
        |08- All queued messages will be held

        |09-----------------------------------------------

        |14Do not attempt to connect during this time.
        |14Do not attempt to monitor the system during
        |14this time.

        |08Maintenance activities include:
        |08- Database optimization
        |08- Log rotation
        |08- Security audits
        |08- System calibration

        |07The board will return to normal operation
        |07automatically at 03:00.

        |12This schedule is non-negotiable.

        |08               — |15AXIOM|08, SysOp
        '''
    }
    {
      number: 5
      title: "Community Directory"
      body:
